{
  "stem": "26983.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other theory, the International Red Cross at that time, the foreign minister in Germany, had some talks with other-- other foreign ministry, maybe to make a separate peace with America.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, well, we can't do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The American Jews want some-- [INAUDIBLE] there are still Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Otherwise there will be no kind of talks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So maybe they wanted to-- to have us for us for this purpose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyhow, there was a selection, only boys between about 12, 13 till 14, 15.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The first selection was done by Hauptsturmfuhrer Schwarzhuber, who was main SS man of Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mengele had a completely different-- he was also Hauptsturmfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was only medical and selection, things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Schwarzhuber was the head of Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was also Hirsch and Kramer, but they were--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, Schwarzhuber wasn't a doctor, SS, a very cruel one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had done most of the selections.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, he hardly killed somebody himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was smaller charges who have done it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Schwarzhuber made a selection of about 90 children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And how did it went?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went-- we had to be naked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, a number, and again, left and right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whoever was there, he was told he can go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, we had a kind of as-if freedom to choose, to choose what?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To go with our parents or whoever was there into the gas chamber, let's say with my father or other people with their parents, or until whatever was left, or to try our luck.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, let's say somebody choose to go out the very first time, or opposite-- a few days later, Mengele made another selection.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe Mengele didn't like it, and said, Schwarzhuber took his job.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
